{"id":941888243,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 month, 4 weeks","timestamp":1682824721,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"5 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/941888243/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Find the Prefix Common Array of Two Arrays","memory":"43.8 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int[] findThePrefixCommonArray(int[] A, int[] B){\n        int n=A.length;\n        int[] check= new int[n+1];\n        int[] ans=new int[n];\n        int idx=0;\n        while(idx<n){\n            int curr=0;\n            check[A[idx]]++;\n            check[B[idx]]++;\n            for(int i=1;i<n+1;i++){\n                if(check[i]>1){\n                    curr++;\n                }\n            }\n            ans[idx]=curr;\n            idx++;\n        }\n        return ans;\n        \n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"find-the-prefix-common-array-of-two-arrays","has_notes":false}
